    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/e5333aef4d174910efd9a896cfbb3cf6.poster.avif?t=1751487156\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/e5333aef4d174910efd9a896cfbb3cf6.webm?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/e5333aef4d174910efd9a896cfbb3cf6.mp4?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你有足够的勇气去超越松树吗？</strong></h2><br><strong>Beyond the Pines</strong> 是一款第一人称、故事驱动的心理恐怖游戏，深入探究主人和他们的狗之间牢不可破的纽带。<br><br>山姆·卡维尔是一位与世隔绝的作家，他在古老的森林中找到了慰藉，并在他心爱的四足朋友洛基（一只获救的德国牧羊犬与比利时马里诺犬杂交）的陪伴下找到了慰藉。 山姆和洛基从洛基还是小狗的时候就形影不离，并肩冒险直到现在……有些东西破坏了他们的联系并将他们分开。<br><br>以威尔士令人难以忘怀的荒野为背景，玩家扮演山姆，踏上一段绝望而又充满情感的旅程，寻找他的同伴并揭开真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/91b8f3877862bbc51b0edd55b895c9dc.poster.avif?t=1751487156\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/91b8f3877862bbc51b0edd55b895c9dc.webm?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/91b8f3877862bbc51b0edd55b895c9dc.mp4?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>洛基在哪里？</strong></h2><br>随着寒冷的夜晚来临，山姆回到了他在森林中僻静的小屋，渴望与他最好的朋友洛基重聚。<br><br>到达后，他有了一个令人震惊的发现——洛基不见了踪影，也没有他下落的迹象。 夜幕降临，狂风呼啸，山姆充满忧虑，并将洛基的失踪归咎于天气。<br><br>但当山姆寻找洛基时，他无法摆脱这样的感觉：松树那边可能潜伏着某种邪恶的东西，正在嘲笑他。<br><br>在一段紧张而充满感情的旅程中，山姆开始揭开真相并寻找他心爱的洛基。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/4ba10f96cc1cd39f1b6e2845db4e2f2e.poster.avif?t=1751487156\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/4ba10f96cc1cd39f1b6e2845db4e2f2e.webm?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/4ba10f96cc1cd39f1b6e2845db4e2f2e.mp4?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>第一人称叙事恐怖体验：扮演山姆·卡维尔，回到他的救援犬——一只德国牧羊犬与比利时玛利诺犬的杂交品种洛基身边，探索他们的故事和纽带。<br><br></li><li>以故事为中心的探索：<strong>Beyond the Pines</strong>鼓励在充满情感的体验中探索环境和构成山姆生活的元素。<br><br></li><li>沉浸式小屋：漫步穿过森林，到达与世隔绝的小屋，但要小心那些可能会跟着你回家的东西。<br><br></li><li>无战斗：<strong>Beyond the Pines</strong> 是故事驱动而非战斗导向，重点关注情感旅程和故事的展开。 然而，您可能会感觉有什么东西在注视着您。<br><br></li><li>情感反思：当山姆面对自己的想法时，你可能会反思并开始质疑自己的情感理智。<br><br></li><li>威尔士民间传说：超越松树受到威尔士民间传说和威尔士美丽风景的影响，为游戏增添了一种怪异而独特的氛围。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/6d2dc23514233348a474d3375361b43e.poster.avif?t=1751487156\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/6d2dc23514233348a474d3375361b43e.webm?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/6d2dc23514233348a474d3375361b43e.mp4?t=1751487156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好踏上一段身临其境的情感之旅，揭开真相并探索山姆和洛基之间牢不可破的纽带。 <strong>Beyond the Pines.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527010/extras/db3ca0c9fe7caf7a933b38a7c6d41eb9.avif?t=1751487156\" width=600 height=132 /></span>",
